# Base URL definition (optional; WebStorm supports variables)
@host = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Create a new meeting
POST {{host}}/meetings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Team Sync",
  "ownerName": "Alice",
  "dateFrom": "2025-05-01",
  "dateTo": "2025-05-05"
}

### 2. Get meeting details (including votes summary)
GET {{host}}/meetings/1

### 3. Add a time option to meeting #1
POST {{host}}/meetings/1/options
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-05-02",
  "hour": 15
}

### 4. Cast a vote for option #1 in meeting #1
POST {{host}}/meetings/1/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "optionId": 1,
  "userName": "Bob"
}

### 5. Re-fetch meeting to see updated summary
GET {{host}}/meetings/1
